- I request: 2 Sheep (2 × 12 = 24)  
- I sacrifice value to encourage acceptance and build rapport for future gain.  
- My resource impact: Wheat (15-5=10), Wood (15-5=10), Sheep (19+2=21)  

[Offer: 5 Wheat, 5 Wood -> 2 Sheep]
